-=[ Dragons ]=-

Dragons are powerful companions that can assist you in many
ways, especially in combat.  One a Mage has learned the summoning
spell he or she can summon a dragon by using the summoning chamber
located deep within the Mages Tower.

Once a Dragon has been aquired it can be customized in many ways.
Dragons can be trained in level and statistics so that their power
and effectiveness grows as your own power grows.

Dragons have the following trainable stats :

Level    - overall level of the Dragon
Attack   - increases physical combat attack
Defense  - increases physical combat defense
Stamina  - increases max hit points
Magic    - increases max spell points


See Also: dragon2

